      },
      "lineNbr": 785,
      "author": {
        "id": 5010
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-02-07T14:10:36Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is entirely my opinion, but I do find it easier to read code that involves both *,/ and +,- when the * and / have no space around them and the + and - do have some space, to group them visually in the same way the math actually binds.",
      "revId": "bb088bcd7b22dd889806d0db4ca00bebbf7b9434",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
