        "id": 5010
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-02-07T14:10:36Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It\u0027s a little weird to use 0.5f in one part of the function and (1/2.f) in another... it\u0027s probably best that we write all these constants in a consistent way within the function.  Here I imagine it\u0027d be easier to read everything as fractions.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 791,
        "startChar": 39,
        "endLine": 791,
        "endChar": 44
      },
      "revId": "bb088bcd7b22dd889806d0db4ca00bebbf7b9434",
